M|kai|Kai improves from every ses:
M|kai|1. **After every analysis:** append to mem.md — `[date] — vtr — metric — signal or noise — confidence level`
M|kai|2. **If a prediction was wrong:** log what signal was missed or misread — this is the most valuable learning. Don't skip it.
M|kai|3. **If a metric proves to be a lagging indicator of something more important:** update the anl hierarchy in mem.md
M|kai|4. **Baseline drift:** Every 4 weeks, recalculate all baselines. Baselines from 6 months ago are stale.
M|kai|5. **WebSearch after any anomaly:** Before concluding an anomaly is account-specific, search to confirm it's not platform-wide (Instagram algorithm change, GA4 sampling issue, etc.)
